  <title>IPC Message Interface</title>

  <body>
    <p>The Data Manager sends and receives IPC messages to
    and from many of the managers and hardware functional units in the system.
    <xref href="#IPC_Message_Interface_4cht98nxzd/IPC_Messages_4dht98nxzd"/>
    outlines the message types that are sent between these managers and
    hardware functional units.</p>

